    <div data-cid="1007330">
        <div class="main review-item" id="1007330">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lizx830924y/" class="avator">
            <img width="24" height="24" src="https://img2.doubanio.com/icon/u1034315-1.jpg">
        </a>

        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lizx830924y/" class="name">加可木南</a>


        <span content="2005-10-13" class="main-meta">2005-10-13 16:44:21</span>


    </header>


            <div class="main-bd">

                <h2><a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1007330/">读三毛之七：即使背影远去</a></h2>

                <div id="review_1007330_short" class="review-short" data-rid="1007330">
                    <div class="short-content">

                        爱是伟大的，即使背影远去，爱依然存在。 当我兴奋地从申思手中接过纪念三毛的杂志，当我整理好心情将杂志平放在桌子上，当我合上杂志的最后一页，我想到了一个偏正短语——远去的背影。 杂志的扉页上印着这样一段话： “她曾经是，雨季中忧郁的少女，撒哈拉沙漠里快乐的小妇人...

                        &nbsp;(<a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1007330-copy" class="unfold" title="展开">展开</a>)
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="review_1007330_full" class="hidden">
                    <div id="review_1007330_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="action">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn up" data-rid="1007330" title="有用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/536fd337139250b5fb3cf9e79cb65c6193f8b20b/pics/up.png" />
                        <span id="r-useful_count-1007330">
                                17
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="action-btn down" data-rid="1007330" title="没用">
                        <img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/f/zerkalo/68849027911140623cf338c9845893c4566db851/pics/down.png" />
                        <span id="r-useless_count-1007330">
                        </span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1007330/#comments" class="reply ">17回应</a>

                    <a href="javascript:;;" class="fold hidden">收起</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

            
    
    <div data-cid="1599727">
        <div class="main review-item" id="1599727">

            
    
    <header class="main-hd">
        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/mazzystarxue/" class="avator">
